"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364e024d70962afbc84f85eaea754ec57b9002ae","tid":1052238,"uid":19725,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HA 醒目<br />\n用一個病人case 打撚到班 咩彭鴻昌、林鄭啞撚左<br />\n一個病人都600萬<br />\n一年5萬個新移民點撚計呀？</span></span>"},{"pid":"41fe964d2e7957048f5e3816bc0d3c6bf600bef4","tid":1052238,"uid":30647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:30:16.000Z","msg":"入稟狀指出，被告因一宗交通意外，2015年11月11日入住伊利沙伯醫院，2017年8月9日轉至九龍醫院，並一直入住至今。惟直至上月28日，被告仍未繳付共約617萬元的醫療費用。院方其間已多次向被告發帳單，九龍醫院更由上月28日開始，每隔3或4天向被告發帳單，惟被告一直拒絕或無法付款，醫管局遂入稟向被告追討欠款，及自上月28日起每日5100元的住院費及相關費用。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀透露，被告的女兒Hu Errong已申請法援，並於2017年就該次交通意外入稟高院，向涉事小巴司機索償。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，秀茂坪2015年11月11日曾發生嚴重車禍，當時兩名持雙程證、分別姓李和姓胡的六旬婦人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑因看錯方向被小巴撞倒</span></span>，其後重傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190308/s00001/1552024554163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190308%2Fs00001%2F1552024554163&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMr0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=92ee0693\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190308%2Fs00001%2F1552024554163&h=f2ad6b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190308/s00001/1552024554163</a>"},{"pid":"9e4a4facc5abfcb31edd36cf4f2c7db59642d680","tid":1052238,"uid":30647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:33:20.000Z","msg":"呢Ｄ擺明懶死唔俾錢又唔走，掉佢係醫院　<br />\n最終結果，又係香港人埋單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b13f17046ef0eb8a0cb10c666ba99e36e0a80e","tid":1052238,"uid":197640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:33:47.